name: Gift Certificate
description:
Now you can give the gift of Gilding Primal Instinct!

When you purchase, you'll receive a lovely business card-sized gift certificate in the mail with a redemption code that can be used at any time here on our online store or by appointment in our NYC studio.

name: Host Prosthetic
description:
Roughly inspired by parasitic organisms, this prosthetic jewelry piece will add just a little bit of primal to your everyday. It is flat-backed and can be applied directly to the skin.

About Prosthetic Jewelry:
Adhered to the skin with medical adhesive or body tape, this new addition to the Gilding Primal Instinct repertoire aims to blur the lines between the body and jewelry. Safe, secure, and completely temporary, these pieces offer a new level of flexibility and customization in adornment

Available in Antiqued Brass or Silver.

This piece comes packaged with protective tissue paper, pouch, and a polishing cloth.

name: Blade Necklace
description: NOW 20% OFF ORIGINAL PRICE! This front-clasping necklace exhibits a perfect balance of intimidation and elegance. The piece features a solid bronze swinging blade pendant, modeled after our couture Chain Guillotine Ring. The blade is coated with black enamel paint and attaches to a single, oxidized copper chain that wraps around the back of the neck and clasps over the sternum.

name: Blade Ring
description: NOW 20% OFF ORIGINAL PRICE! This double-finger ring, can make any hand look like a brutal weapon. Made of oxidized bronze, the piece spans half the hand with a fan-like blade designed to reference our couture Chain Guillotine Ring. The blade stands up about an inch from the knuckle, making a real statement without being overly cumbersome. It is finished with black enamel paint along the blade, and the entire thing is sealed with a coat of clear lacquer. Each side of this double finger ring is approximately a size 7. The open space allows the piece to more flexibly fit a range of finger sizes.

name: Conviction Ring
description: NOW 20% OFF ORIGINAL PRICE! Prepare to pass judgement with the Conviction Ring. Made of oxidized bronze and sealed with clear lacquer, this tapered spike ring makes a subtle but aggressive statement. The piece features design elements from our couture See No, Hear No, Speak No Series, and can be worn in the direction of the finger or facing backward over the knuckle. This ring is made in a size 7. To special order this piece in another size, simply select the "Custom Size" option when placing your order. We will contact you within 24 hours to confirm your desired size. Please note, sizing may take up to 5 additional business days prior to shipping.

name: Frayed Necklace
description: NOW 20% OFF ORIGINAL PRICE! This necklace features hammered dome medallions attached to three oxidized copper chains that clasp at the back of the neck. As the necklace cascades down the chest, the classical design transitions into a deconstructed cotton that continues down the torso. Fashioned after our couture See No, Hear No, Speak No Series, this piece is sure to grab attention!

name: Frayed Earring
description: These earrings feature small hammered dome medallions that transition into delicate deconstructed cotton. Fashioned after our couture See No, Hear No, Speak No Series, they're elegant enough for a cocktail party and grungy enough for a dive bar. Ear wire and post backings are made of sterling silver.

name: Trio Ring
description:
NOW 20% OFF ORIGINAL PRICE!

This elegant, yet unsettling ring is made of oxidized bronze and features three organically shaped prongs that wrap around the finger. Ending in three blackened bowls that sit on top of the finger, this is a unique and captivating piece.

This ring is made in a size 7. To special order this piece in another size, simply select the "Custom Size" option when placing your order. We will contact you within 24 hours to confirm your desired size. Please note, sizing may take up to 5 additional business days prior to shipping.

name: Ribcage Body Chain
description: NOW 20% OFF ORIGINAL PRICE! We are proud to introduce the first collaborative collection between Gilding Primal Instinct and FYI by Dani Read! Featuring a spine shaped plate attached to several chains extending around the torso, the piece can be worn in the front or back depending on personal preference. It is finished in a beautiful, high-polished rhodium plating. This piece is made to order and may take up to 4 weeks to ship.

name: Ribcage Cuff
description: NOW 20% OFF ORIGINAL PRICE! We are proud to introduce the first collaborative collection between Gilding Primal Instinct and FYI by Dani Read! Meant to be worn as either decorative accessory or light bondage, these bracelets feature an inconspicuous ring that can be used to attach the bracelets to each other or anything else you can imagine! The piece is finished in a beautiful, high-polished rhodium plating.
